{"tid":2312132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"送foodpanda 送到爆頭 Iphone 唔見埋","createTime":"2020-12-04T15:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T10:42:50.000Z","uid":326805,"like":46,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"47a5cdd330caba21ff055a476e9344280c89b16f","tid":2312132,"uid":326805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:25:53.000Z","msg":"呢幾日開始送foodpanda, 諗住做下外快<br />\n今日第二日送, 第一張單無咩野, 都係行1.5公里<br />\n第二單叫我由大圍金獅花園行去希爾頓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾15分鐘我左右, 我已經急步行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但夠鐘都係行左5成, 佢即刻cut單加停我30分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就租左共享單車, 諗住可以快啲送第三單<br />\n<br />\n一睇, 屌10分鐘由大圍去希爾頓攞餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻踩快啲, 去到一個天橋 (之後救護員嚟到同我講經常有人呢度炒)<br />\n已經少少放慢, 但原來有個位底下有舊障礙<br />\n上面枝黃色棒無左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後成部車飛起, 當我有反應, 塊面已經「嘭!!!」落左地滑行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到醫院, 左面有4個OK大傷口,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加灰係, 洗完傷口出嚟, iphone唔見左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去find my iphone 搵唔到, 但打電話打得通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用desktop on whatsapp web 係on到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有三個問題想請教<br />\n<br />\n1. 點樣可以減低疤痕 (或者hopefully 無疤痕...)?<br />\n2. 有無辦法知道iphone 係邊?<br />\n3. foodpanda 話俾保險我claim, 但打開條link 無左, 咩玩法?<br />\n<br />\n今日有少少灰, 任何想寸我屌9我 搞無謂gag 可唔可以下次先<br />\n小弟認真想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b295f116e22c73c22d756c5b05dcc4320f1e4d0d","tid":2312132,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:36:58.000Z","msg":"咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a0c30732714a9aaf1480017c41fe5804c909e","tid":2312132,"uid":7722,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw foodpanda 而家有限時取餐？<br />\n但15分鐘大圍去到希爾頓應該要跑過去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcd8cc341e73261812d4fec6a1e1a318b3fc81e","tid":2312132,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"真係慘"},{"pid":"a841d573384fd366756c2e6eb626e37f71abfd9d","tid":2312132,"uid":326805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e32a0c30732714a9aaf1480017c41fe5804c909e","tid":2312132,"uid":7722,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw foodpanda 而家有限時取餐？<br />\n但15分鐘大圍去到希爾頓應該要跑過去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"應該係有啲單有 <br />\n而你唔知你張單會唔會好strict<br />\n結果最後張單遲42分鐘, 佢先cancel我"},{"pid":"1898ffcc76f7dbdb108c84e9ec7f6a832d22aa5e","tid":2312132,"uid":76514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:40:24.000Z","msg":"好慘 幫推"},{"pid":"5ddf5944be877915399e93dabd2d06d0bf64693d","tid":2312132,"uid":369015,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T15:40:26.000Z","msg":"15分鐘大圍金獅花園行去希爾頓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你又真係同佢癲"},{"pid":"3def03a72a1f852a57c7957d7ece62dd37440117","tid":2312132,"uid":201604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":1